58460362e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989548587597046, \"rank\": 0.0007656788915960273, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"the 27-year-old athletebecame\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"the most decorated gymnast\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around finals\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory marked a comeback for Biles, who withdrew from the last summer Olympics in 2021 due to her mental health.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The victory\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"a comeback\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"the last summer\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her withdrawal from the competition, Vance appeared onFox News'Outnumberedin July 2021, where he called out the media for supporting Biles during her \\\"weakest moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her withdrawal\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"onFox News'Outnumberedin\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"weakest moment\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's understandable that she was going through an incredible amount of pressure,\\\" the Ohio senator said at the time.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\", \"score\": 0.999441442962045, \"rank\": 0.0005570304424745661, \"text\": \"Ohio\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible amount\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I find so weird about this - and it reflects on the media more than it does on Simone Biles - is that we have tried to turn a very tragic moment, Simone Biles quitting the Olympic team, into this act of heroism.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"a very tragic moment\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"this act\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"heroism\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think it reflects pretty poorly on our sort of therapeutic society that we try to praise people not for moments of strength, not for moments of heroism, but for their weakest moments.\\\"\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sort\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"therapeutic society\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"heroism\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"their weakest moments\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vance continued: \\\"Being an athlete at that level is incredibly tough.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vance\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A normal response in this moment would be to say: 'It's just a shame that she's going through this.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A normal response\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"just a shame\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shame that she quit.'\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shame\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But instead, what our press has done, I think, is turn this into this weird therapeutic moment.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our press\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"this weird therapeutic moment\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Let us praise her for doing this.'\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 1998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think that's really where the problem herein lies.\\\"\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, Bilespulled out of the women's all-around gymnastics competitionto focus on her mental health, after suffering from acondition known as the \\\"twisties\\\".\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's all-around gymnastics competitionto focus\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"acondition\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"twisties\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The phenomenon, typically experienced by gymnasts, involves losing control mid-air and feeling unable to land the move, creating a high-risk and dangerous situation.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The phenomenon\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"the move\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-risk and dangerous situation\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has previously described the twisties as being \\\"lost in the air,\\\" likening the uncomfortable experience to being unable to drive while at the wheel in a car.\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"the uncomfortable experience\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the wheel\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"a car\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, that all went away during Tuesday's all-around team final, when Biles scored her eighth Olympic medal - becoming the most decorated gymnast in the US and the fifth-most decorated female Olympic gymnast in the world.\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2734, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989548587597046, \"rank\": 0.0007656788915960273, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"her eighth Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"the most decorated gymnast\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"the fifth-most decorated female Olympic gymnast\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not the first time that past comments made by Vance have resurfaced sincehe was selected as former president Donald Trump's running matein the 2024 presidential election.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 2921, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4455366490534854e-14